{"tid":1743010,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"出事！支那內蒙鼠疫失控 軍警關卡封鎖全省","createTime":"2019-11-21T04:29:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T02:52:45.000Z","uid":32511,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"d5684b619982dda545a261f727b9e47edf5970d9","tid":1743010,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:29:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2QCS5e4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2QCS5e4&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameHpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=04118874\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2QCS5e4</a><br />\n<br />\n中國官方雖然宣稱鼠疫疫情已經在控制範圍內，然而內蒙古官方數據又出現第三例病例<br />\n <br />\n然而牆內的狀況是，內蒙對外道路的關卡都有公安駐守嚴格控管出入。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FWbyAL6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFWbyAL6.jpg&h=d3466120&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"013c1a85b39cbe13880a59b8c40fb317bc468946","tid":1743010,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:30:07.000Z","msg":"香港金融業職工總會（香港金總）將於星期六舉行特別會員大會，以商討政治工業行動事宜。本會已根據香港金總會章，於2019年11月18日以電郵通知本會會員召開特別會員大會事宜。詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n特別會員大會<br />\n日期：2019年11月23日<br />\n時間：下午5時至8時<br />\n地點：尖沙咀金巴利道25號長利商業大廈12樓1202室<br />\n備註：<br />\n -  請出席之會員提早15分鐘前來登記，以便準時開始。<br />\n -  會場內，除大會攝影師外，不得拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n大會開始前一小時(下午4時至5時)亦有招收會員活動。請各會員及有意者撥冗出席。如有任何查詢，請透過telegram (@HKFUnion)或面書與工會成員聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n請準會員預先填寫入會表格：<br />\n中: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FJRRvX5t488CyQVPYA&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameHpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=71b068f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA</a><br />\neng: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FBmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameHpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=09b94380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5</a><br />\n<br />\n工會Facebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKFUnion%2F&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameHpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=1677e76f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/</a><br />\n工會Telegram channel：<a href=\"https://t.me/HKFIEGU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKFIEGU&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameHpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=15b2c261\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKFIEGU</a><br />\n<br />\n#特別會員大會"},{"pid":"61840de27b668b875ec77944613ee48cd93c6233","tid":1743010,"uid":238370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:38:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af9f1c93e1491dc92a02541aee9f2e1f8952bbcf","tid":1743010,"uid":24465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:40:31.000Z","msg":"支爆近了"},{"pid":"225b1e381b978ad9fb3346ffd481d007b66cd188","tid":1743010,"uid":4942,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:44:57.000Z","msg":"支那人死清光 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1778715026c25d762190841cea41f6d2301250bb","tid":1743010,"uid":48531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:45:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecb22c3dacee9e554cfb639dfcad59b5ed8e8a8e","tid":1743010,"uid":300165,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d5684b619982dda545a261f727b9e47edf5970d9","tid":1743010,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:29:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2QCS5e4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.co